{"title":"Centos维护Nginx","slug":"Linux-Centos维护Nginx","date":"2020-11-11T15:47:13.000Z","updated":"2020-11-20T13:22:38.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Linux-Centos维护Nginx.json","excerpt":null,"covers":null,"content":"<p>进入维护目录：<code>cd /usr/local/nginx/sbin</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight jboss-cli\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">./nginx</span> -v 查看当前nginx版本号</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">./nginx</span> -s stop 关闭</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">./nginx</span> 开启</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">./nginx</span> -s <span class=\"keyword\">reload</span> 重新加载配置文件（修改配置文件后进行）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>安装目录：<code>/usr/local/nginx/sbinx</code></p>\n","more":"<p>进入维护目录：<code>cd /usr/local/nginx/sbin</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight jboss-cli\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">./nginx</span> -v 查看当前nginx版本号</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">./nginx</span> -s stop 关闭</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">./nginx</span> 开启</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">./nginx</span> -s <span class=\"keyword\">reload</span> 重新加载配置文件（修改配置文件后进行）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>安装目录：<code>/usr/local/nginx/sbinx</code></p>\n","categories":[{"name":"Linux","path":"api/categories/Linux.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"linux","path":"api/tags/linux.json"},{"name":"nginx","path":"api/tags/nginx.json"}]}